        "Description": "While backpacking in Europe, 23-year-old Craig Stewart is befriended by a local woman, Louise Voll, in Berlin. But Louise has been hired by a Moroccan mercenary squad to slip Stewart party drugs laced with a neurotoxin at a seedy nightclub, and to extract him with the help of some of the nightclub security. The next morning, Stewart is missing.",
